Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.20,0:00:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們是開朗的洗車工\N無論哪種車都會洗得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.40,0:00:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,閃閃亮亮，光光滑滑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.27,0:00:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我們完全都不閃亮\N只是個配角...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.58,0:00:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,別想了，別想了，別想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.78,0:00:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我們不是發誓過\N別再去想這些了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.45,0:00:19.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回想一下那天的夕陽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.88,0:00:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有過那樣嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.99,0:00:31.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是的，洗車場怎麼會出現戰車呢\N(日文"洗車"與"戰車"同音)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.13,0:00:32.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的，真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.39,0:00:33.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼會這樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.86,0:00:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的，真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.03,0:00:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,叫負責人給我滾出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.24,0:00:52.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,銀河天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:53.58,0:00:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼？為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.72,0:00:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,危機，這下糟糕了\N緊張！緊張！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.42,0:01:02.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻煩光線  BURU  BURU
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.29,0:01:04.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大騷動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.53,0:01:07.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,ok，胡鬧一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.60,0:01:11.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也沒關係，吃個飲茶\N好啊！好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.13,0:01:13.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱著歡悅的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.37,0:01:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最後一起向神明祈禱吧\NBANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.54,0:01:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因果報應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.24,0:01:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每天都是冒險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.84,0:01:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一旦開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.98,0:01:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它順其自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.32,0:01:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒有機關，沒有魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.85,0:01:36.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,孤注一擲的I.N.G.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.19,0:01:38.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,無憂無慮的狂歡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.66,0:01:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夢想與希望的機關鎗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.30,0:01:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,鎖定想要的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.70,0:01:47.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,BANG  BANG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳舞吧，玩吧\NBRAVO！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.44,0:01:53.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐上令人興奮的火箭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.17,0:02:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開闢天下無敵的成功之路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.96,0:02:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(天使罐頭附加炮塔)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.87,0:02:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位觀眾早安\N又到了DEJIKO的新聞時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.60,0:02:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,首先的新聞是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.47,0:02:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了，不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.94,0:02:29.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,城市某處的研究所研發的\N最新型戰車被偷走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.08,0:02:33.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傷腦筋啊，大事不妙了\N銀河天使隊救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.28,0:02:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,難得的假期又泡湯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.09,0:02:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過奇怪的人還真多\N竟然會去偷戰車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，我知道了\N犯人一定是佛特啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.63,0:02:50.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她那麼喜歡收集武器\N這下事件解決了，工作結束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.21,0:03:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，這樣就事件解決\N工作結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.41,0:03:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，這個是真的戰車耶\N真的戰車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.81,0:03:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,動了，動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.08,0:03:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是高興的時候啊\N梅爾優，要快點讓它停下來才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.29,0:03:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？我不是高興，而是很開心喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.89,0:03:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，請快點想個辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.63,0:03:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.36,0:03:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(沒人在＋開心＝)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.37,0:03:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以高興嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.74,0:03:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我聽不懂妳在說什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.74,0:03:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為裡面沒有人在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.61,0:03:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.44,0:03:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊...這裡是諾麥德，諾麥德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.75,0:03:43.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心愛的香草\N收到我愛的電波了嗎？請說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.48,0:03:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,執行死刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.85,0:03:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的，遵命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開玩笑，開玩笑的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發現目標戰車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.53,0:03:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,現在行經阿恰拉大道\N往南南西方向狂飆中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.89,0:03:57.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的腦袋也快要狂飆了\N香草救救我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.80,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.43,0:04:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思，不好意思\N忘記切掉電源了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.70,0:04:07.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好了！香草，薄荷和梅爾優\N竟然在那台被偷的戰車上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.58,0:04:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從以前就覺得她們是\N討厭的小孩和騙人的天然笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.21,0:04:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒想到會鬧出\N如此可怕的大事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.95,0:04:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,開什麼玩笑，我在跟你道歉\N你竟敢把話題轉到別的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.29,0:04:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特，我覺得應該不可能...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.73,0:04:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看來只好直接去確認了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.13,0:04:31.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行啦，絕對不能開槍喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.27,0:04:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來，停下來啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.47,0:04:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行，煞車和方向盤都沒反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.74,0:04:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，薄荷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.48,0:04:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什麼事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.88,0:04:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,問妳一個問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.38,0:04:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這台戰車的前方\N到底有什麼在等待著它呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.15,0:04:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一、小怪獸，二、中怪獸\N三、大怪獸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.82,0:04:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.96,0:05:00.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猜錯了，正確答案是\N四、建設中的道路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.36,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我笑不出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.57,0:05:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，那是真的怪獸耶，怪獸\N我們運氣真好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.27,0:05:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,運氣用錯地方了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.95,0:05:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看起來比微波爐還難操作耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.45,0:05:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,沒關係\N給它狠狠地按下去吧，狠狠地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.92,0:05:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣啊\N那就恭敬不如從命了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.83,0:05:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,加油啊，梅爾優\N在這危機時刻想要逃出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.03,0:05:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只能靠梅爾優過人的好運了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.71,0:05:45.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彎曲航法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.05,0:05:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,為什麼戰車要彎曲航法啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.28,0:05:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不過，這還蠻好玩的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.62,0:06:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且一點意義都沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.20,0:06:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行了，沒想到連梅爾優的好運\N也無法讓它停下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.67,0:06:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接著就會朝海邊全速前進\N我們就會死翹翹，漂浮在海面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.17,0:06:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？可是我沒帶泳衣來耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.35,0:06:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.78,0:06:28.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.95,0:06:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.18,0:06:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣就可以去買泳衣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.79,0:06:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,漂亮地掉入我設下的絕佳陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.76,0:06:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,佛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.73,0:06:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳這樣不對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.10,0:06:50.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳好不容易拚了命偷來的戰車\N怎麼可以隨便放著不管呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是就算再怎樣\N喜歡飛彈或武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.91,0:06:58.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把這麼大的戰車偷走\N看來佛特妳真的很喜歡這些喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.05,0:07:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.05,0:07:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放開我，放開我\N我是冤枉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.92,0:07:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布魯特斯，沒想到連你也是\N(羅馬凱撤大帝的心腹)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.92,0:07:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大概是搞錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雖然主謀者已經抓到了\N但是你們身為現行犯的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能輕易地消除
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.66,0:07:19.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,迅速丟下武器快點投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.83,0:07:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情好像變複雜了\N我們先投降吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.41,0:07:32.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...老實認錯賠罪的話\N法官也會同情你們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.88,0:07:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,笨蛋....\N又不是卡通，打中的話怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對啊，對啊\N還有許多事情還沒做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.82,0:07:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我才不要這樣就死掉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.52,0:07:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是誰啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.79,0:07:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這種問題，請先透過我的律師好嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.36,0:07:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這樣不行啊，薄荷\N就算蘭花再怎麼不講理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也不能拿大砲射她呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.87,0:07:59.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是我啊\N大概是戰車自己射的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.87,0:08:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？那這台戰車討厭蘭花嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.08,0:08:08.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,錯，正確答案是它最討厭我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.15,0:08:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你到底是誰啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.99,0:08:13.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我就老實告訴妳吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.09,0:08:15.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是60年來\N專心致力於戰車研發
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.46,0:08:18.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,傳說中的南．阿佐谷博士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.39,0:08:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要掉下去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.80,0:08:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,掉下去就死定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.47,0:08:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你已經逃不掉了\N快點跟我回研究所吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.30,0:08:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是你們，是那台戰車啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.67,0:08:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.41,0:08:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情就發生在\N距現在12小時5分30秒之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我像往常般地\N一邊吃著宵夜的牛丼便當
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.35,0:08:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一邊努力製造戰車\N結果突然出現了一個妖精說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.36,0:08:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，好帥的叔叔啊\N你太帥了，我就給你一個願望吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.97,0:09:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被這麼說的我\N毫不迷惑地只說了一句話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.77,0:09:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,"我想要一台活戰車"\N本來沒有抱著多大的希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.67,0:09:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,結果真是不可思議啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.04,0:09:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的戰車竟然代替我\N吃起宵夜牛丼便當了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.41,0:09:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，太好了，我的戰車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.28,0:09:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這謊言太多破綻了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.35,0:09:22.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為開發自動型武器\N是國家機密呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.82,0:09:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我如果說出來是會被罵的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.76,0:09:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,對...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.00,0:09:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我們的努力全都白費了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.47,0:09:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...我不知道耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.30,0:09:37.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果能見到妖精就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.91,0:09:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,事情總算可以解決\N任務結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.01,0:09:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎麼了？\N戰車先生你肚子痛嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰車沒有肚子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,戰車先生不太高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.97,0:10:15.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？這也是沒辦法的呀\N戰車在街上亂走的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.38,0:10:15.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,會造成大家困擾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.88,0:10:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是它好不容易自由了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.28,0:10:22.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它大概也想做許多開心的事\N也想吃許多好吃的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.92,0:10:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯...還有，還有...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.29,0:10:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,梅爾優
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.06,0:10:32.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蘭花，香草\N我說的話很怪嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.76,0:10:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不會奇怪啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,這是我們的工作呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.97,0:10:42.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為是工作\N所以就什麼都可以做嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.47,0:10:43.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.27,0:10:48.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因為和戰車先生\N或許可以成為好朋友啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.98,0:11:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就這樣，討人厭的小鬼\N和騙人的天然笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.32,0:11:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,從現在起成為\N我這個戰車大王的人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.46,0:11:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，等等，你別跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果再動就殺人質\N如果再動就殺人質...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.16,0:11:13.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小妹妹，妳的腹語說得不錯嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.20,0:11:18.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,薄荷，薄荷\N我們現在變成人質了耶，人質
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.84,0:11:21.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，這齣感人的戲劇竟然會...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.45,0:11:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(戰爭還沒結束，持續進行)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.82,0:11:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是跟你說了我沒做嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.12,0:11:36.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃豬排丼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你聽我說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要吃天婦羅丼嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.73,0:11:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.70,0:11:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妳要吃豬排丼是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.20,0:11:44.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是亂七八糟啊\N(這邊的爭戰也是持續進行)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.50,0:11:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,彎曲航法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.77,0:11:49.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下個菜單是\N「猴子救援昆布」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.43,0:12:20.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,滿天的星辰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.23,0:12:25.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,像是打翻水瓶似的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.51,0:12:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躺在新月下的吊床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.31,0:12:35.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作了夢之後，變得想見你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,側耳傾聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.12,0:12:46.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你看，不是聽見了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.16,0:12:50.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,令人興奮的天線
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.03,0:12:54.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就讓它睡著吧  NO  NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.17,0:13:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,處女座的我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.18,0:13:06.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向牡羊座的你發出信號\N急電，急電
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.15,0:13:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,乘著飛馬的翅膀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.25,0:13:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,前去迎接你
